    <item>
      <title>“交易浪潮”有望提振私募股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/wall-street-beat-01-31-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Houlihan Lokey 直接配售和二级市场主管 Matt Swain 表示，私募股权公司即将收获大笔利润。他在“彭博公开市场”上表示，许多投资者在公开市场配置过多资金，这为私募股权行业抓住“交易浪潮”提供了契机。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/wall-street-beat-01-31-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼承诺废除加拿大碳税，该税似乎已死</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大针对消费燃料征收的国家碳税可能即将进入最后几周，此前接替总理贾斯汀·特鲁多担任自由党领袖的两位主要候选人均承诺废除该税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-carbon-tax-appears-dead-after-carney-pledges-to-scrap-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺特称赞欧洲央行在控制物价且不影响就业方面取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/knot-hails-ecb-progress-in-taming-prices-without-hit-to-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特表示，欧洲央行已成功将通胀率从历史高位回落，且没有对欧元经济及其民众造成严重损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/knot-hails-ecb-progress-in-taming-prices-without-hit-to-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
